reviews.review_text:
"...some people up in treetops just a lookin for their kites..." just had to listen to the "3 Playin in the Band's" show..Jerry is blistering ..the 'Rider" is on fire...This is Primo Garcia Humboldt Private Stash Bro...man If I had a time machine...I bet Bobby is wearin' shorts and  the pony tail! 
That's what I love about the Dead..I was concerened about something earlier but while listening my blues just blow away...WOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO HOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOOO
